Title: Flawed Study of Ph.D. Production
Body: Date: Tue, 10 Dec 1996 15:07:48 GMT Server: NCSA/1.4.2 Content-type: text/html Last-modified: Mon, 25 Sep 1995 07:37:18 GMT Content-length: 6002 Flawed Study of Ph.D. Production Massy-Goldman report alleging 50% CSE Ph.D. overproduction to be re-issued due to flawed data July 28, 1995 During the first two weeks of July, a study of Ph.D. production by William F. Massy of Stanford and Charles A. Goldman of RAND received widespread attention, stimulated by a New York Times article.
